title: Activate The Right Genes | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Activate The Right Genes | Joel Osteen
description:
No negative cycle can keep you from the good things God wants to do in your life. When you activate the spiritual genes passed down from your Heavenly Father, you'll have everything you need to fulfill your destiny. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
